title: HTC One A9 Review An Android-Powered iPhone 6 Thats $250 Cheaper
text:
HTC One A9 Review: An Android-Powered iPhone 6 That's $250 Cheaper 
Christian Post Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
A screengrab from a video report on the hands-on experience with the HTC One A9. The HTC One A9 reviews are saying the new smartphone is just like an Android-powered iPhone 6, only $250 cheaper than the Apple device.One of the most noticeable things about the HTC One A9 is its eerie similarity to the iPhone 6.
